viewData.name: Bridal Style Eyelashes 23
viewData.short_description: The PhiNesse eyelashes are natural and handmade. Each eyelash is made to look as natural as possible.
viewData.long_description: The PhiNesse eyelashes are natural and handmade. Each eyelash is made to look as natural as possible. The eyelashes are soft, flexible, easy to apply and comfortable to wear. Specially designed to enhance the make-up look, and to emphasize the eyes even more. They can make a noticeable difference, but they also give a natural look, so most people do not realize that you wear artificial lashes.
